Description: Rest on the Flight into Egypt. Woody landscape with Holy family seated at centre, the Virgin taking fruit from a basket at left; within an emblematical frame with putti and several symbols (IHS. zodiac, pentagram, chiro); second state with number; after Spranger Engraving
Producer name: Print made by: Aegidius Sadeler II
